|--------------------------------------------------(0x01)-------(changelog)--|

--[06.Dec.2013] .alyn.post. -
    + migrate to git.
    + update email address and website url.
    + remove rcsid.

--[28.Jun.2006] .alyn.post. -
    + document mkdep.
    + finish README.b00t documentation.
    + add b00t.c, a simple lisp interpreter.
    + add remaining files in distribution to test target.
    + update mksystype for several linux platforms.

--[22.Jun.2006] .alyn.post. -
    + add more documentation to README.b00t.
    + add TODO file listing future work.

--[20.Jun.2006] .alyn.post. -
    + remove all references to automeek from config.db.
    + remove *-sys targets from config.db.  i've never used them.

--[18.Jun.2006] .alyn.post. -
    + add README.b00t in anticipation of importing b00t.c.  i haven't
      finished the documentation for every routine yet.
    + shut up compiler warnings by renaming main to func in forarg.c
    + remove all references to lace and savant from config.db.
    + minor gentoo fixes in config.db.
    + create an |opt| pdesc for installing software into /opt.
    + add conf-ld-so to config.db, containing the extension we expect
      for shared libraries--preliminary support for shared libraries
      on darwin.
    + remove cross compilation support from config.db, it never
      worked properly in the first place.
    + add -Wno-missing-braces to all devel-style gcc lines in
      config.db.  when we statically allocate system-defined
      structures, (like jmp_buf) we can't portably get our braces
      correct.
    + add -fno-strict-aliasing to all gcc lines in config.db.
    + improve freebsd and redhat systype detection.  use the correct
      perl on freebsd.

--[24.Feb.2005] .alyn.post. -
    + actually include mkstring in the release. (oops)
    + add mkdep utility

--[13.Dec.2004] .alyn.post. -
    + makeutil version 0.2.0 released

--[10.Dec.2004] .alyn.post. -
    + switch dist target to use openssl for md5 and sha1 checksums.
      openssl is available on a wider variety of platforms.
    + continuing documentation cleanup

--[09.Dec.2004] .alyn.post. -
    + oof, included an old version of config.c.  updated to one
      that actually works with config.db
    + the extract format text archive is now bzip2 compressed
    + better documentation in the README
    + update web page

--[01.Dec.2004] .alyn.post. -
    + add mkstring utility
    + minor correction to testarray.c

--[28.Nov.2004] .alyn.post. -
    + makeutil version 0.1.0 released


